<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Hi <%= @candidate.first_name %>,
    </p>

    <p>
      You now have an interview request! Interview requests are created by employers, recruiters, and other members of the CardinalHire platform. Go to your <%= link_to "Dashboard", new_user_session_url %> to review your interview requests.
    </p>

    <p>
      This opportunity comes from an interested employer:
      <p><%= @user.first_name %>&nbsp;<%= @user.last_name %></p>
      <p>Company Size: <%= @user.company_size %></p>
      <p>Employer Hiring Location: <%= @user.employer_hiring_location %></p>
      <p>Employer Roles: <%= @user.employer_roles %></p>
      <p>Employer Roles Type: <%= @user.employer_roles_type %></p>
      <p>Employer Remote Status: <%= @user.employer_remoteness %></p>
    </p>

    <p>
      Once you accept an interview request, a CardinalHire Account Manager will be in contact with you about the details of your candidacy.
    </p>

    <p>
      In a hurry to get started? Contact your CardinalHire Account Manager directly via email. <%= mail_to "alex@cardinalhire.com" %>
    </p>

    <p>
      For more information and to opt-out or manage your subscriptions, visit our <%= link_to 'website', 'https://www.cardinalhire.com' %> or contact us.
    </p>

    <p>
      Contact Team<br />
      CardinalHire.com
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
